Attribution
-----------

This project uses data from:
- JMdict (Japanese-Multilingual Dictionary) by the EDRDG
- https://www.edrdg.org/wiki/index.php/JMdict-EDICT_Dictionary_Project

The original JMdict data has been processed and curated for this application.
Modifications include:
- Extraction of katakana-only entries
- Addition of phonetic pattern classifications
- Wasei-eigo detection and annotation
- Categorization for learning purposes

